    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>This recipe takes around 5-<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>10 min to prep, so get your casserole dish and all your ingredients ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Make sure your dish is oven-proof and safe to use on the hob. Don't have one? Start cooking in a large, wide-based pan then transfer to an oven-proof dish and cover tightly with foil</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-creamy-horseradish-smoked-basa-tortiglioni/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-creamy-horseradish-smoked-basa-tortiglioni/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> and <strong>crushed garlic </strong>to the dish</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-creamy-horseradish-smoked-basa-tortiglioni/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> smoked basa</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-creamy-horseradish-smoked-basa-tortiglioni/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and the<strong> chopped basa</strong> to the dish with your <strong>horseradish</strong>,<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> tortiglioni</strong>, a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[750ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Nestle the tortiglioni into the water as much as you can, then stir everything together and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-creamy-horseradish-smoked-basa-tortiglioni/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the pasta is cooked through</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Tip: Give everything a stir halfway through for evenly cooked pasta!</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-creamy-horseradish-smoked-basa-tortiglioni/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the tortiglioni is nearly cooked, chop your <strong>dill</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Once cooked, remove the dish from the oven and add the <strong>spinach</strong>,<strong> creme fraiche</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped dill</strong> (save some for garnish!) and gently stir until the spinach starts to wilt and the fish is cooked through \u2013 this is your <strong>one pot creamy horseradish smoked basa tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-creamy-horseradish-smoked-basa-tortiglioni/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one pot creamy horseradish smoked basa tortiglioni </strong>and garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped dill</strong> and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
